時就會有觸電的感覺。其實，只要改用延長線，MacBook 自漏電問題就能夠馬上就解決。因為延長線擁有導電鐵片，在與變壓器的地線連接後就能有效導電，令全鋁外殼上的電流就可沿地線走自然離開，也能避免觸電的情況發生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/03/23/macbookmega/tips-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F03%2F23%2Fmacbookmega%2Ftips-2%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97YeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=cfcb5431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/03/23/macbookmega/tips-2/</a>"},{"pid":"c0c445b21c77af2060e2084666ffbc60334288f3","tid":2458151,"uid":50423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a7d342a03b45fbf5d71e8cb6b77eca185135d91f","tid":2458151,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"317392c44daddb0dc693002f5f6c3c852afa041c","tid":2458151,"uid":50423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4669fb1cb6ad7da424219a89d949dfeb78bbfa92","tid":2458151,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:26:29.000Z","msg":"去買條延長線就解決晒<br />\n一係就插牆身電掣叉電"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:29:19.000Z","msg":"點解用延長線就冇事? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"用延長線就搞掂<br />\n後來有網民發現三腳插頭轉換器上的地線端是絕緣的，根本沒有跟變壓器上的地線端接駁起來，所以碰到 MacBook 時就會有觸電的感覺。其實，只要改用延長線，MacBook 自漏電問題就能夠馬上就解決。因為延長線擁有導電鐵片，在與變壓器的地線連接後就能有效導電，令全鋁外殼上的電流就可沿地線走自然離開，也能避免觸電的情況發生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/03/23/macbookmega/tips-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F03%2F23%2Fmacbookmega%2Ftips-2%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97YeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=cfcb5431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/03/23/macbookmega/tips-2/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"原來APPLE咁ON9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17ac471198f2d5184e4b3b2a7d07a8c44999d1a","tid":2458151,"uid":88886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:34:30.000Z","msg":"你隻火牛都冇水線梗係電到你升天啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4021f319bd22918f0acc927880a0bf11b86b18","tid":2458151,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:36:32.000Z","msg":"1) 有機會係電感而唔係漏電。<br />\n以金屬外殼最明顯，差電期間近距離絕緣接觸的不論人體/金屬都會因為高電勢相鄰而產生類似電容原理嘅電感效應。<br />\n簡單講你無直接通電，不過因為近個差緊電嘅位而自體產生電位差。 你就算呢個時間攞條電線幫個殼接地都應該會繼續有感覺。<br />\n<br />\n低電壓差得慢就應該唔會再有感覺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2) 真係漏電。<br />\n正常金屬外殼內部都會接地，確保你有用正常嘅3腳插頭。 咁有漏嘅就會經條接地線走而唔係經個身。呢個情況係接咗地就會無感覺"},{"pid":"bbfec10e899fae4a3c4ff52ff2bbfae373253bb1","tid":2458151,"uid":88886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c0c445b21c77af2060e2084666ffbc60334288f3","tid":2458151,"uid":50423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a7d342a03b45fbf5d71e8cb6b77eca185135d91f","tid":2458151,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"317392c44daddb0dc693002f5f6c3c852afa041c","tid":2458151,"uid":50423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:29:19.000Z","msg":"點解用延長線就冇事? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:31:48.000Z","msg":"用延長線就搞掂<br />\n後來有網民發現三腳插頭轉換器上的地線端是絕緣的，根本沒有跟變壓器上的地線端接駁起來，所以碰到 MacBook 時就會有觸電的感覺。其實，只要改用延長線，MacBook 自漏電問題就能夠馬上就解決。因為延長線擁有導電鐵片，在與變壓器的地線連接後就能有效導電，令全鋁外殼上的電流就可沿地線走自然離開，也能避免觸電的情況發生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/03/23/macbookmega/tips-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F03%2F23%2Fmacbookmega%2Ftips-2%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97YeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=cfcb5431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/03/23/macbookmega/tips-2/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"原來APPLE咁ON9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited